<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-account-of-take-into-account">take account of / take ... into account</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>考虑到；把……考虑进去：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company takes account of environmental issues wherever possible. 
只要有可能，这家公司都会考虑到环境问题。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One must take the audience into account when making speeches. 
人们在演讲时必须要考虑听众。</p></div></div>